      "level": 2,
      "path": "/nara/travel_ai/app/main.py",
      "content": "The Journey Books \u2014 WhatsApp Automation Bot FastAPI Application Entry Point Endpoints: - POST /webhook/evolution \u2014 receives all WhatsApp messages from Evolution API - POST /webhook/sheets \u2014 receives PAID/KILL/PAUSE signals from Google Sheets - GET /health \u2014 health check - GET /api/settings \u2014 get bot settings - POST /api/settings \u2014 update bot settings - GET /api/leads \u2014 list leads - POST /api/leads/{id}/kill \u2014 toggle kill switch - POST /api/leads/{id}/pause \u2014 toggle pause switch"
    },
