      "path": "/nara/travel_ai/app/services/llm.py",
      "content": "LLM Router \u2014 Multi-provider LLM with automatic fallback. Supports: - Gemini (Google) \u2014 great for testing, generous free tier - Grok (xAI) \u2014 fast, good for production - OpenAI \u2014 GPT-4o-mini, reliable fallback - Ollama \u2014 local LLMs, no API key needed Uses LangChain's unified interface so structured output, guardrails, and conversation history all work identically regardless of which provider is active. Set LLM_PROVIDER in .env to switch providers."
    },
